Come home to beauty and serenity in a one-of-a-kind Santa Barbara Highlands condominium. This 1 bedroom 1 bathroom with loft unit includes: new paint, new front door, new kitchen (appliance ready), vaulted beam ceiling (tongue & groove), laminate flooring & much more. The unit also includes one carport with plenty of storage and guest parking nearby. The Santa Barbara Highlands HOA amenities include: 2 pools, shower rooms, spa, sauna and a large clubhouse. Location, location, location! With a short walk or bike ride to the beach, the harbor, Santa Barbara City College or downtown Santa Barbara this is by far one of the most desirable locations to live in Santa Barbara.
